name: The sun is rising
description:
Celebrating 500k objkt on HEN

Amaterasu is the highest deity in Japanese mythology. In the most famous legend, she shuts herself away in a cave, bringing disasters to both the world and heaven... Celebrating 500k object on HEN.

Apart from that, the name means “to shine in heaven,” and this can be what this goddess encourages us to do: let our own light shine 🌻
